## Visual

A parchment-style infographic poster arranged as eight numbered panels above a bottom “social replay loop” timeline, framed by ornate manuscript borders. It uses navy, gold, cream, and dark red with serif typography, illuminated medieval-style figures, religious iconography, and symbolic diagrams of attention, memory, institutions, norms, and transmission. The visuals combine saint-like scribes, icons, arrows, circular feedback loops, scales, networks, books, chalices, hearts, and institutional symbols to present social memory as a quasi-mechanical and ritualized process.
